                    <h1>Does it worth your time?</h1>
                    <p class="indent">Children of Morta is a narrative driven roguelike where you play a total of seven
                        characters,
                        each with his own mechanics and playstyle. The campaign is short and the story will progress
                        even when your character dies. Most of the achievements will need grinding but are straight
                        forward and do not require you to become expert on the game.</p>
                    <h2>First Playthrough</h2>
