                        specific achievements. Fully exploring the dungeons on every run will save you a lot of
                        post-story grinding. Nine achievements are main story related. Seven are unlocked from finishing
                        the side quests that are dungeon specific. Getting all family members to level 20 will earn you
                        four achievements. You mailnly have to worry for

